translate ru TheWarIsLost_12cfbdff:
    # "The exhaustion had forced her to sleep, but the crude shaking of a cart now roughly woke her."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_67a06d30:
    # "She might have slept, but Sarah still felt exhausted."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_22ae6557:
    # "She was lying on her stomach, she could feel her breasts press against the hard wooden floor of the cart."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_b70167eb:
    # "Her hands were still bound behind her back. She wore a blindfold, but it had begun to shift, allowing her to peek through with one eye."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_81187630:
    # "The ropes that bound her had begun to cut into her wrists."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_3765100b:
    # "All across her skin she could feel the wooden surface of the cart. She realized she was still fully naked."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_0ce70353:
    # "An oppressive heat filled the air in the cart."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_fb784740:
    # "As she tried to move, Sarah felt something straining against her throat. It took her a moment to understand she was still wearing the collar."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_aab7cad2:
    # "The wagon suddenly stopped, causing Sarah to roll around the wooden floor."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_9b520f44:
    # "The door to the cart flew open. Sarah stared up and saw the officer standing in the doorway."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_aa18ad10:
    # "Looking past him, Sarah saw the star-filled night sky."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_77b2cf0b:
    # "By now, the officer had come to understand that talking didn't achieve much, and so he simply grabbed Sarah without saying anything."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_aa6be1ad:
    # "Still bound, he held onto her arm and guided her out of the cart."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_0e1ac133:
    # "As soon as Sarah stepped out, she felt her feet sinking into the sands of the desert. She had never felt anything like it."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_894d51a0:
    # "The sand felt like a warm blanket around her ankles."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_e3eeb3b5:
    # "Above them, the stars shone brighter than Sarah had ever seen before in her life."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_9e3ef85a:
    # "The officer dragged Sarah out towards a camp fire, where several other soldiers were sitting."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_1f759afb:
    # "As they noticed her coming closer, some began to howl and jeer at her."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_a7c7f54f:
    # "Sarah did her best to ignore them."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_0c185d8b:
    # "It was hard to look dignified, fully naked and bound, Sarah realized."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_9256276f:
    # "The officer pulled a dagger from his belt, and for a moment, Sarah felt her heart freeze."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_253771bc:
    # "But the officer had no ill intent, and instead, slashes through the bindings on her wrists, freeing her hands."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_cd253a8f:
    # "Sarah rubbed her wrists, a much needed relief from the pain of being tied up."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_b5d5ba8a:
    # s "Thank you."
    s ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_eee5f4f7:
    # "The officer only looked at her confused."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_e89a5cf5:
    # "Sarah looked around the campfire, and saw that all the men had their eyes on every part of her. She did her best to cover herself, but the men never looked away."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_96949cbe:
    # "The officer said some things at her, emoting towards a large black cast iron pot, sitting on the fire."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_6ebefdb3:
    # "Sarah didn't understand, but the officer kept up, finally verbalizing a few broken words."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_d118eb2b:
    # "Officer" "You...cook."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_4c686089:
    # "Sarah felt a wave of relief coming over her. Her mind had imagined many worse things by now."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_1dba0af9:
    # "Almost grateful, she nodded excessively at the officer."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_f4cd4631:
    # "The officer showed her some cooking utensils, a dull knife, a ladel, a large wooden spoon, and a hand full of ingredients."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_4c00c2b1:
    # "Sarah had never been a great cook, but she imagined even her cooking couldn't be bad enough to justify injury, and so she committed herself to the task."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_f1b91390:
    # "Though Sarah still had no clothes on, she found it easier to forget her shame when she was busy working."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_ed91359b:
    # "From the corner of her eyes, she could see the men still looked at her, but by now it was more incidental than constant."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_f6eef826:
    # "Sarah chopped up some of the vegetables, adding them into the pot."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_7a942e9e:
    # "For a moment, she thought about using the dull knife to fight herself to freedom, but she quickly realized that the idea was absurd."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_0626bb3b:
    # "There were close to twenty soldiers, each massive in size and armed with real weapons and armor."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_bec06af2:
    # "Even in the impossible chance that she did overcome them, it would just leave her stranded in the middle of a desert."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_93ed0633:
    # "She shook her head and forgot the laughable idea."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_ddf3b804:
    # "Adding to the soup, Sarah chopped up some of the pork that was available and cooked it over a spit."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_2288a021:
    # "She was almost happy, having a task to set her mind too, and for a moment, she did forget where she was."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_c171ca52:
    # "Eventually, the soldiers seemed content with the smell and were unwilling to wait for their food any longer."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_a47ad53c:
    # "Sarah had to admit to herself, even she had begun to salivate at the smell of the food she had prepared."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_f769ad07:
    # "The officer motioned for her to serve them, and with the ladel in hand, Sarah poured out some soup and cut off some pork for each soldier."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_7a2e29cd:
    # "As she went around the circle, each soldier smiled a broad smile at her. Some more daring, ran a hand up her leg."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_904b1c77:
    # "One soldier went so far as to smack Sarah on her ass after she served him his food, causing the rest to break out laughing."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_44303334:
    # "Sarah felt the shame burn on her face, but she ignored the insult and carried on."
