translate ru TheWarIsLost_0929327c:
    # "He protected her, Sarah knew that much, but there seemed to be limits to how far he was willing to go in restraining his own men."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_3cbaa3ff:
    # "Finally, having served the last soldier, Sarah went to grab a bowl for herself."
