translate ru TheWarIsLost_54e8406d:
    # "She had managed to eat no more than two spoonfuls when she felt a small rock hitting her body."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_83e58347:
    # "Sarah looked up, startled, and saw one of the soldiers near her waving for her attention."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_2d697a45:
    # "The man was older looking, a large grey beard, and he held out his bowl of food, still half full."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_6395f4da:
    # "Sarah looked across the campfire, and saw the officer was distracted, discussing something with another soldier."
    ""

translate ru TheWarIsLost_52742edd:
    # "She began walking over to the soldier and reached out, but just as she almost grabbed the bowl, the man pulled it back and shook his finger."
